title: Big Drama At Bobby’s House + Should Amy’s Daughter Be Allowed To Do This? + 90’s Famous First Lines Game
itunes:title: Big Drama At Bobby’s House + Should Amy’s Daughter Be Allowed To Do This? + 90’s Famous First Lines Game
description:
Bobby talks about the drama regarding decorating his new house and something his girlfriend wants to put on the wall. Amy is struggling with letting her daughter sleep in on the weekends. Plus, we celebrate two famous 90’s country artists' birthdays with a fun game where we have to guess the first line of famous 90’s songs!
